description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Bacillo virgola del Koch; Bacillus cholerae; Bacillus cholerae-asiaticae; Kommabacillus; Liquidivibrio cholerae; Microspira comma; Pacinia cholerae-asiaticae; Spirillum cholerae; Spirillum cholerae-asiaticae; Vibrio albensis; Vibrio cholera; Vibrio cholerae biovar albensis; Vibrio cholerae bv. albensis; Vibrio cholerae-asiaticae; Vibrio comma.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
